Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 1600/92 of 15 June 1992 concerning specific measures  for the Azores and Madeira relating to certain agricultural products  (13), as last amended by  Regulation (EC) No 3290/94, and in particular Articles 10 and 24 (6) thereof,
